            <paragraph>Sets the size of a margin used to expand the drawable rect of this <strong>CanvasGroup</strong>. The size of the <strong>CanvasGroup</strong> is determined by fitting a rect around its children then expanding that rect by <reference internal="True" refid="class-canvasgroup-property-fit-margin"><inline classes="std std-ref">fit_margin</inline></reference>. This increases both the backbuffer area used and the area covered by the <strong>CanvasGroup</strong> both of which can reduce performance. This should be kept as small as possible and should only be expanded when an increased size is needed (e.g. for custom shader effects).</paragraph>
